Global Citrus Seed Market Insights
Citrus Seed Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Citrus Seed Market Overview
The global citrus seed market size was valued at approximately USD 1.15 billion in 2024 and is expected to expand at a CAGR of 6.4% from 2025 to 2032. The increasing demand for citrus fruits for juice production and the growing awareness regarding the nutritional value of citrus products are driving market growth. Additionally, the rising popularity of plant-based food products and the growing use of citrus seeds in various applications such as cosmetics and pharmaceuticals further support the demand for citrus seeds. The market is witnessing innovation in citrus seed processing, promoting greater utilization in multiple industries.

